code: import httpService from'./httpService';export var productService={getProducts:getProducts,getProductById:getProductById,deleteProduct:deleteProduct,saveProduct:saveProduct,getEmptyProduct:getEmptyProduct};function getProducts(){var filterBy=arguments.length>0&&arguments[0]!==undefined?arguments[0]:'';console.log('gettin products..');if(filterBy){var name=filterBy.name;var query="?txt=".concat(name);return httpService.get("product/".concat(query));}else{return httpService.get("product/");}}function getProductById(_id){return httpService.get("product/".concat(_id));}function deleteProduct(_id){return httpService.delete("product/".concat(_id));}function _updateProduct(product){return httpService.put("product/".concat(product._id),product);}function _addProduct(product){return httpService.post("product",product);}function saveProduct(product){return product._id?_updateProduct(product):_addProduct(product);}function getEmptyProduct(){return{name:'',email:'',phone:''};}
